edu.cs495.engine.game

Class AbstractGameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cs495.engine.game.AbstractGameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractItem, AbstractPhysicalGameObject, AbstractScenery, Anvil, ChatConsole, ChatTextbox, ChatView, Fountain

    public abstract class AbstractGameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract game object features several attributes which are shared across all game objects used for updating and rendering.
    Version:
    February 2019
    Author:
    Spencer Imbleau
